        "text_wGJeWV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At PureGrubs, we started with a simple mission — to bring honest, high-quality nutrition to backyard chickens while supporting American farmers, workers, and families.We saw the growing flood of imported insect products from overseas — often labeled as “natural” but with no real transparency or quality control. That didn’t sit right with us. We believed there had to be a better way.<br/>So, we rolled up our sleeves and decided to grow our own Black Soldier Fly Larvae (BSFL) right here in the USA. No middlemen. No overseas factories. Just clean, sustainable, nutrient-rich grubs — raised under our watch, with care and consistency.<br/>What began as a small, bootstrapped idea in a garage — a few bins, a lot of late nights, and a deep belief in doing things the right way — has grown into a brand trusted by chicken owners nationwide. Every bag of PureGrubs supports American jobs, local agriculture, and the values that built this country: hard work, integrity, and pride in what we make.<br/>We don’t take shortcuts, and we don’t compromise on quality. From our farm to your flock, PureGrubs stands for freshness, honesty, and American-made excellence — because your chickens deserve the best, and so does our country.<br/>PureGrubs — Bugs Feed the World. Made Right Here at Home. 🇺🇸</p>",
